                        README
                        ------


This repository contains scripts to do the following:
	i.	obtain data from collectd csv files
	ii.	obtain data from ActiveState Stackato via stackato
		command line.
	iii.	write above data into BUS files (BUS Format),
		a format that is required for presenting
		in (HP) vPV tree-maps.

                     DEPENDENCIES
                     ------------

The scripts rely on the following settings and perl modules:
	i.	csv plugin is enabled in collectd.conf file
	ii.	perl modules Text::CSV and Text::CSV_XS
		modules are installed
	iii.	stackato command-line is installed

                       TESTING
                       -------

The scripts have been tested to work with ActiveState Stackato
micro-cloud version 2.4.3.

                       RUNNING
                       -------

Run the script 'createbusfiles' (shell script).
